ckground-color: rgb(242, 241, 241); color: rgb(143, 143, 143); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, Simsun, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; font-family: &#39;Courier New&#39;; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">3.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; font-family: &#39;Courier New&#39;; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">创建&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">/etc/subversion/passwd&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">文件，该文件包含了用户授权的详细信息</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(242, 241, 241); color: rgb(143, 143, 143); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, Simsun, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-weight: bold; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">$&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-weight: bold; font-family: &#39;Courier New&#39;; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">sudo&nbsp;htpasswd&nbsp;-c&nbsp;/etc/subversion/passwd&nbsp;user_name</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(242, 241, 241); color: rgb(143, 143, 143); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, Simsun, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; font-family: &#39;Courier New&#39;; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">它会提示您输入密码，当您输入了密码，该用户就建立了。<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">“-c”</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">选项表示创建新的</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">/etc/subversion/passwd</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">文件，所以</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">user_name</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">所指的用户将是文件中唯一的用户。如果要添加其他用户，则去掉</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">“-c”</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">选项即可：</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">$</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; font-family: &#39;Courier New&#39;; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;sudo&nbsp;htpasswd&nbsp;/etc/subversion/passwd&nbsp;other_user_name</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(242, 241, 241); color: rgb(143, 143, 143); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, Simsun, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">4.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; font-family: &#39;Courier New&#39;; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">您可以通过下面的命令来访问文件仓库：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(242, 241, 241); color: rgb(143, 143, 143); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, Simsun, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; font-family: &#39;Courier New&#39;; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">$&nbsp;svn&nbsp;co&nbsp;http://hostname/svn/myproject&nbsp;myproject&nbsp;--username&nbsp;user_name</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(242, 241, 241); color: rgb(143, 143, 143); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, Simsun, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">或者通过浏览器：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-weight: bold; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">http://hostname/svn/myproject</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(242, 241, 241); color: rgb(143, 143, 143); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, Simsun, STHe', '', 'svn', 0, '', 0, '0');
INSERT INTO `onethink_cms_document_article` VALUES (51, '<p>采集大家都遇到，从一个文章详情页获取到一组数据 如title、description、content、cover。</p><p>然后我就遇到了客户提出的将采集图片入库的问题（以前项目遇到过，存本地没完美解决）。</p><p>我们知道tp 里有一个完整的上传类Upload。上传流程是：表单A-&gt;提交B操作里，B调用上传类处理上传。</p><p>然后知道上传的时候PHP缓存了 然后 通过is_uploaded_file() 检测，move_uploaded_file 去移动这个缓存。</p><p>我们先试着组装$_FILES 去调用上传类：</p><pre><code class=\"php hljs\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; overflow-x: auto; color: rgb(77, 77, 76); border-radius: 0px; font-family: monaco, Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Courier, monospace; background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(137, 89, 168);\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-function\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(137, 89, 168);\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(66, 113, 174);\">upload_remote</span><span class=\"hljs-params\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(245, 135, 31);\">()</span></span>{\r\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(142, 144, 140);\">//设置 上传类的相关配置</span>\r\n    $model = <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(113, 140, 0);\">\'Picture\'</span>;\r\n   <span class=\"hljs-comment\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(142, 144, 140);\">/* 调用文件上传组件上传文件 */</span>\r\n   $driver = C(<span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(113, 140, 0);\">\"{$model}_UPLOAD_DRIVER\"</span>);\r\n    Slog::log($driver);\r\n   $upload_config = C(<span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(113, 140, 0);\">\"{$model}_UPLOAD\"</span>);\r\n    $upload_config[<span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(113, 140, 0);\">\'driver_config\'</span>] = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(137, 89, 168);\">null</span>;\r\n   Slog::log($upload_config);\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(142, 144, 140);\">//模拟上传数组</span>\r\n   $remote = <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(113, 140, 0);\">\'http://car0.autoimg.cn/car/upload/2015/2/6/t_20150206093016381497110.jpg\'</span>;\r\n   $tmp_name = tempnam(IS_SAE? SAE_TMP_PATH:sys_get_temp_dir(), <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(113, 140, 0);\">\'jpg\'</span>);\r\n    $temp = file_put_contents($tmp_name, file_get_contents($remote));\r\n   Slog::log(<span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(113, 140, 0);\">\'写入文件\'</span>);\r\n    Slog::log($temp);\r\n   $_FILES = [\r\n     <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(113, 140, 0);\">\'remote\'</span>=&gt;[\r\n        <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(113, 140, 0);\">\'name\'</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; =&gt; <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(113, 140, 0);\">\'t_20150206093016381497110.jpg\'</span>,\r\n       <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(113, 140, 0);\">\'type\'</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; =&gt; <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(113, 140, 0);\">\'image/jpeg\'</span>,\r\n        <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(113, 140, 0);\">\'size\'</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; =&gt; filesize($tmp_name),\r\n       <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(113, 140, 0);\">\'tmp_name\'</span> =&gt; $tmp_name,\r\n       <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(113, 140, 0);\">\'error\'</span> &nbsp; &nbsp;=&gt;<span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(245, 135, 31);\">0</span>\r\n      ]\r\n   ];\r\n    Slog::log($_FILES);\r\n   $Upload = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(137, 89, 168);\">new</span> Upload($upload_config, $driver, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(137, 89, 168);\">null</span>);\r\n    $info &nbsp; = $Upload-&gt;upload($_FILES);\r\n   <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(137, 89, 168);\">if</span>(!$info){\r\n     Slog::log($Upload-&gt;getError());\r\n      <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(137, 89, 168);\">return</span> $Upload-&gt;getError();\r\n    }\r\n   <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(137, 89, 168);\">return</span> $info;\r\n }<br></code></pre><p>这时候，上传类的相关信息是这样的：</p><p><img alt=\"Clipboard Image.png\" src=\"https://attachments.tower.im/tower/8d0b58080b77414f955796d88e4726a5?version=auto&amp;filename=Clipboard%20Image.png\" width=\"817\" height=\"774\" data-image-size=\"817,774\"><br></p><p>我去找了上传类的报错：</p><p><img alt=\"Clipboard Image.png\" src=\"https://attachments.tower.im/tower/63270a1eabd8481cbbb3d4afe3969c3d?version=auto&amp;filename=Clipboard%20Image.png\" width=\"436\" height=\"389\" data-image-size=\"436,389\"><br></p><p>我们看一下$file[\'tmp_name\'] 是不是和组装的$_FILES[\'remote\'][\'tmp_name\'] 一样</p><p><img alt=\"Clipboard Image.png\" src=\"https://attachments.tower.im/tower/8e427132b8a8446fad77a29e432cb1d1?version=auto&amp;filename=Clipboard%20Image.png\" width=\"765\" height=\"177\" data-image-size=\"765,177\"><br></p><p>看来就是is_uploaded_file 不认这个文件。</p><p>这个表现和 表单加密类型不是multipart/form-data 一致：</p><p><img alt=\"Clipboard Image.png\" src=\"https://attachments.tower.im/tower/6088517373b9497b9840de40138f75e6?version=auto&amp;filename=Clipboard%20Image.png\" width=\"668\" height=\"133\" data-image-size=\"668,133\"><br></p><p>我就去找找php如何识别表单的加密类型</p><p>找到一篇 关于这个类型的漏洞<a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/xuzuning/article/details/7444709\" target=\"_blank\">PHP multipart/form-data 远程DOS漏洞</a></p><p>受这篇的启发，我决定去看看这个is_uploaded_file php函数的源码，我下了一个php.5.5.31 和当前使用的版本最接近</p><p>然后st 打开解压后的源码，搜索is_uploaded_file 关键字：</p><p><img alt=\"Clipboard Image.png\" src=\"https://attachments.tower.im/tower/d5f9c730db2745869572ce049cd31158?version=auto&amp;filename=Clipboard%20Image.png\" width=\"960\" height=\"743\" data-image-size=\"960,743\"><br></p><p>搜索到一个定义和几个测试，既然有测试 我先看看 测试里什么样的测试是通过的：</p><pre><code class=\"php hljs\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; overflow-x: auto; color: rgb(77, 77, 76); border-radius: 0px; font-family: monaco, Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Courier, monospace; background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">-TEST--\r\nrfc1867 max_file_uploads - <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(137, 89, 168);\">empty</span> files shouldn<span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(113, 140, 0);\">\'t count (debug version)\r\n--SKIPIF--\r\n<!--?php if(!function_exists(\"leak\")) print \"skip only for debug builds\"; ?-->\r\n--INI--\r\nfile_uploads=1\r\nerror_reporting=E_ALL\r\nmax_file_uploads=1\r\n--POST_RAW--\r\nContent-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=---------------------------20896060251896012921717172737\r\n-----------------------------20896060251896012921717172737\r\nContent-Disposition: form-data; name=\"file2\"; filename=\"\"\r\nContent-Type: text/plain-file\r\n\r\n\r\n-----------------------------20896060251896012921717172737\r\nContent-Disposition: form-data; name=\"file3\"; filename=\"\"\r\nContent-Type: text/plain-file\r\n\r\n33\r\n-----------------------------20896060251896012921717172737\r\nContent-Disposition: form-data; name=\"file4\"; filename=\"file4.txt\"\r\nContent-Type: text/plain-file\r\n\r\n\r\n-----------------------------20896060251896012921717172737\r\nContent-Disposition: form-data; name=\"file1\"; filename=\"file1.txt\"\r\nContent-Type: text/plain-file\r\n\r\n1\r\n-----------------------------20896060251896012921717172737--\r\n--FILE--\r\n<!--?php\r\nvar_dump($_FILES);\r\nvar_dump($_POST);\r\nif (is_uploaded_file($_FILES[\"file1\"][\"tmp_name\"])) {\r\n var_dump(file_get_contents($_FILES[\"file1\"][\"tmp_name\"]));\r\n}\r\n?-->\r\n--EXPECTF--\r\nNotice: No file uploaded in Unknown on line 0\r\n\r\nNotice: No file uploaded in Unknown on line 0\r\n\r\nWarning: Uploaded file size 0 - file [file4=file4.txt] not saved in Unknown on line 0\r\narray(4) {\r\n&nbsp; [\"file2\"]=&gt;\r\n&nbsp; array(5) {\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; [\"name\"]=&gt;\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; string(0) \"\"\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; [\"type\"]=&gt;\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; string(0) \"\"\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; [\"tmp_name\"]=&gt;\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; string(0) \"\"\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; [\"error\"]=&gt;\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; int(4)\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; [\"size\"]=&gt;\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; int(0)\r\n&nbsp; }\r\n&nbsp; [\"file3\"]=&gt;\r\n&nbsp; array(5) {\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; [\"name\"]=&gt;\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; string(0) \"\"\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; [\"type\"]=&gt;\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; string(0) \"\"\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; [\"tmp_name\"]=&gt;\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; string(0) \"\"\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; [\"error\"]=&gt;\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; int(4)\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; [\"size\"]=&gt;\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; int(0)\r\n&nbsp; }\r\n&nbsp; [\"file4\"]=&gt;\r\n&nbsp; array(5) {\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; [\"name\"]=&gt;\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; string(9) \"file4.txt\"\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; [\"type\"]=&gt;\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; string(0) \"\"\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; [\"tmp_name\"]=&gt;\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; string(0) \"\"\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; [\"error\"]=&gt;\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; int(5)\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; [\"size\"]=&gt;\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; int(0)\r\n&nbsp; }\r\n&nbsp; [\"file1\"]=&gt;\r\n&nbsp; array(5) {\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; [\"name\"]=&gt;\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; string(9) \"file1.txt\"\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; [\"type\"]=&gt;\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; string(15) \"text/plain-file\"\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; [\"tmp_name\"]=&gt;\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; string(%d) \"%s\"\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; [\"error\"]=&gt;\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; int(0)\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; [\"size\"]=&gt;\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; int(1)\r\n&nbsp; }\r\n}\r\narray(0) {\r\n}\r\nstring(1) \"1\"\r\n</span><br></code></pre><p>从测试结果看出 当前file1.txt 内容未1，size为1，是通过测试</p><pre><code style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; border-radius: 0px; font-family: monaco, Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', Courier, monospace; background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">is_uploaded_file($_FILES[\"file1\"][\"tmp_name\"])</code></pre><p>的</p><p>并且注意到他的tmp_name 是没有路径的，那么我把临时文件写如php的自带上传目录试试呢？</p><p>结果也是不行的。</p><p>后来找到上传相关的那个标准：RFC1867.c</p><p>看不懂，找了鸟哥的介绍php怎么处理文件上的<a href=\"http://www.laruence.com/2009/09/26/1103.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.laruence.com/2009/09/26/1103.html</a></p><p><a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/xuzuning/article/details/7444709\" target=\"_blank\">如何curl上传文件</a></p><p>后来请了新浪的大牛高方宇帮我看这个问题，他找到了这个函数的源码</p><p><img alt=\"Clipboard Image.png\" src=\"http://jaylabs-blog.stor.sinaapp.com/Uploads/Editor/2016-01-08/568fae77da95f.\" data-image-size=\"690,264\"><br></p><p>&gt;rfc1867_uploaded_files 是一个哈希表，存了上传文件的路径，如果是空或者不在这表里面 就返回false</p><p>&gt;然后我grep了一下对这个哈希表的所有操作</p><p>&gt;其他都是判断操作，只有main/rfc1867.c:        zend_hash_add_ptr(SG(rfc1867_uploaded_files), temp_filename, temp_filename); 这个是往里面添加了</p><p>&gt;这个应该是request时候对post坐初始化的时候的操作。 应该是没提供给上层php函数来修改这个表了</p><p>&gt;不用扩展在上层应该没有api弄了<br><br>所以得出的结论是，没有办法hack 模拟post file 在不开扩展不经过http请求的情况下。</p><p>最后就又回到了我开始最初的写法，不去用上传类判断，直接用驱动上传：</p><pre class=\"lang-php\" data-lang=\"php\">//将远程图片保存到sae\r\npublic function save_pic_to_storage($url, $name){\r\n $ext = explode(\'.\', $url);\r\n  $ext = array_pop($ext);\r\n $tmp_name = tempnam(on_sae()? SAE_TMP_PATH:sys_get_temp_dir(), $ext);\r\n file_put_contents($tmp_name, file_get_contents($url));\r\n  $file = [\r\n   \'savepath\'  =&gt; \'picture/\',\r\n   \'savename\' =&gt; $name.\'.\'.$ext,\r\n    \'tmp_name\'  =&gt; $tmp_name,\r\n  ];\r\n  $sae = new \\org\\upload\\driver\\Sae(array_merge(c(\'picture_upload\'), [\'domain\'=&gt;\'upload\']));\r\n if($sae-&gt;save($file, true)){\r\n   return $file[\'url\'];\r\n  }else{\r\n    trace($sae-&gt;getError());\r\n   return $url;\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n</pre><p>以上代码基于tp5 beta版所写。想我80w的图片，如果都走一次http请求得多慢啊。计算了要10t存储空间，sae storage 免费10g 放不下，而且要扩展得年会员1w。反正这些图片原型里没用到，汽车之家没防盗链，用他们的流量吧。</p>', '', 'tp5,thinkphp,采集', 0, '', 0, '0');
INSERT INTO `onethink_cms_document_article` VALUES (52, '<p class=\"vcard author\" style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; color: rgb(85, 102, 119); font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">作者：&nbsp;<a class=\"fn url\" href=\"http://www.ruanyifeng.com/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; text-decoration: none; border: none; color: rgb(85, 102, 119);\">阮一峰</a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; color: rgb(85, 102, 119); font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">日期：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.ruanyifeng.com/blog/2012/08/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; text-decoration: none; border: none; color: rgb(85, 102, 119);\">2012年8月25日</a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">喜欢写Blog的人，会经历三个阶段。</p><blockquote style=\"margin: 2em; padding: 1em; list-style-type: none; border: 1em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240); font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &#39;Andale Mono&#39;, monospace; border-top-left-radius: 20px; border-top-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-left-radius: 20px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　第一阶段，刚接触Blog，觉得很新鲜，试着选择一个免费空间来写。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　第二阶段，发现免费空间限制太多，就自己购买域名和空间，搭建独立博客。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　第三阶段，觉得独立博客的管理太麻烦，最好在保留控制权的前提下，让别人来管，自己只负责写文章。</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">大多数Blog作者，都停留在第一和第二阶段，因为第三阶段不太容易到达：你很难找到俯首听命、愿意为你管理服务器的人。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\"><img src=\"http://image.beekka.com/blog/201208/bg2012082501.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0.7em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); border-top-left-radius: 0.7em; border-top-right-radius: 0.7em; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.7em; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.7em;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">但是两年前，情况出现变化，一些程序员开始在<a href=\"https://github.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; color: rgb(17, 34, 51);\">ｇithub</a>网站上搭建blog。他们既拥有绝对管理权，又享受github带来的便利----不管何时何地，只要向主机提交commit，就能发布新文章。更妙的是，这一切还是免费的，github提供无限流量，世界各地都有理想的访问速度。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">今天，我就来示范如何在github上搭建Blog，你可以从中掌握github的Pages功能，以及Jekyll软件的基本用法。更重要的是，你会体会到一种建立网站的全新思路。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\"><img src=\"http://image.beekka.com/blog/201208/bg2012082502.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0.7em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); border-top-left-radius: 0.7em; border-top-right-radius: 0.7em; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.7em; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.7em;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 800;\">一、Github Pages 是什么？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">如果你对编程有所了解，就一定听说过<a href=\"https://github.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; color: rgb(17, 34, 51);\">github</a>。它号称程序员的Facebook，有着极高的人气，许多重要的项目都托管在上面。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">简单说，它是一个具有版本管理功能的代码仓库，每个项目都有一个主页，列出项目的源文件。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\"><img src=\"http://image.beekka.com/blog/201208/bg2012082503.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0.7em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); border-top-left-radius: 0.7em; border-top-right-radius: 0.7em; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.7em; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.7em;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">但是对于一个新手来说，看到一大堆源码，只会让人头晕脑涨，不知何处入手。他希望看到的是，一个简明易懂的网页，说明每一步应该怎么做。因此，github就设计了<a href=\"http://pages.github.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; color: rgb(17, 34, 51);\">Pages功能</a>，允许用户自定义项目首页，用来替代默认的源码列表。<span style=\"font-weight: 800;\">所以，github Pages可以被认为是用户编写的、托管在github上的静态网页。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\"><img src=\"http://image.beekka.com/blog/201208/bg2012082504.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0.7em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); border-top-left-radius: 0.7em; border-top-right-radius: 0.7em; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.7em; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.7em;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">github提供模板，允许<a href=\"https://help.github.com/articles/creating-pages-with-the-automatic-generator\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; color: rgb(17, 34, 51);\">站内生成</a>网页，但也允许用户自己编写网页，然后上传。有意思的是，这种上传并不是单纯的上传，而是会经过Jekyll程序的再处理。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 800;\">二、Jekyll是什么？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 800;\"><a href=\"http://jekyllrb.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; font-weight: normal; border: none; color: rgb(17, 34, 51);\">Jekyll</a>（发音/&#39;dʒiːk əl/，&quot;杰克尔&quot;）是一个静态站点生成器，它会根据网页源码生成静态文件。</span>它提供了模板、变量、插件等功能，所以实际上可以用来编写整个网站。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\"><img src=\"http://image.beekka.com/blog/201208/bg2012082505.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0.7em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); border-top-left-radius: 0.7em; border-top-right-radius: 0.7em; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.7em; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.7em;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 800;\">整个思路到这里就很明显了。你先在本地编写符合Jekyll规范的网站源码，然后上传到github，由github生成并托管整个网站。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">这种做法的好处是：</p><blockquote style=\"margin: 2em; padding: 1em; list-style-type: none; border: 1em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240); font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &#39;Andale Mono&#39;, monospace; border-top-left-radius: 20px; border-top-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-left-radius: 20px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　* 免费，无限流量。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　* 享受git的版本管理功能，不用担心文章遗失。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　* 你只要用自己喜欢的编辑器写文章就可以了，其他事情一概不用操心，都由github处理。</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">它的缺点是：</p><blockquote style=\"margin: 2em; padding: 1em; list-style-type: none; border: 1em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240); font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &#39;Andale Mono&#39;, monospace; border-top-left-radius: 20px; border-top-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-left-radius: 20px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　* 有一定技术门槛，你必须要懂一点git和网页开发。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　* 它生成的是静态网页，添加动态功能必须使用外部服务，比如评论功能就只能用<a href=\"http://disqus.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; color: rgb(17, 34, 51);\">disqus</a>。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　* 它不适合大型网站，因为没有用到数据库，每运行一次都必须遍历全部的文本文件，网站越大，生成时间越长。</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">但是，综合来看，它不失为搭建中小型Blog或项目主页的最佳选项之一。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 800;\">三、一个实例</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">下面，我举一个实例，演示如何在github上搭建blog，你可以跟着一步步做。为了便于理解，这个blog只有最基本的功能。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">在搭建之前，你必须已经安装了<a href=\"http://git-scm.com/book/en/Getting-Started-Installing-Git\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; color: rgb(17, 34, 51);\">git</a>，并且有<a href=\"https://github.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; color: rgb(17, 34, 51);\">github</a>账户。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 800;\">第一步，创建项目。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">在你的电脑上，建立一个目录，作为项目的主目录。我们假定，它的名称为jekyll_demo。</p><blockquote style=\"margin: 2em; padding: 1em; list-style-type: none; border: 1em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240); font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &#39;Andale Mono&#39;, monospace; border-top-left-radius: 20px; border-top-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-left-radius: 20px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　$ mkdir jekyll_demo</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">对该目录进行git初始化。</p><blockquote style=\"margin: 2em; padding: 1em; list-style-type: none; border: 1em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240); font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &#39;Andale Mono&#39;, monospace; border-top-left-radius: 20px; border-top-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-left-radius: 20px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　$ cd jekyll_demo</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　$ git init</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">然后，创建一个没有父节点的分支gh-pages。因为github规定，只有该分支中的页面，才会生成网页文件。</p><blockquote style=\"margin: 2em; padding: 1em; list-style-type: none; border: 1em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240); font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &#39;Andale Mono&#39;, monospace; border-top-left-radius: 20px; border-top-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-left-radius: 20px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　$ git checkout --orphan gh-pages</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">以下所有动作，都在该分支下完成。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 800;\">第二步，创建设置文件。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">在项目根目录下，建立一个名为_config.yml的文本文件。它是jekyll的设置文件，我们在里面填入如下内容，其他设置都可以用默认选项，具体解释参见<a href=\"https://github.com/mojombo/jekyll/wiki/Configuration\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; color: rgb(17, 34, 51);\">官方网页</a>。</p><blockquote style=\"margin: 2em; padding: 1em; list-style-type: none; border: 1em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240); font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &#39;Andale Mono&#39;, monospace; border-top-left-radius: 20px; border-top-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-left-radius: 20px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　baseurl: /jekyll_demo</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">目录结构变成：</p><blockquote style=\"margin: 2em; padding: 1em; list-style-type: none; border: 1em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240); font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &#39;Andale Mono&#39;, monospace; border-top-left-radius: 20px; border-top-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-left-radius: 20px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　/jekyll_demo<br/>　　　　|--　_config.yml</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 800;\">第三步，创建模板文件。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">在项目根目录下，创建一个_layouts目录，用于存放模板文件。</p><blockquote style=\"margin: 2em; padding: 1em; list-style-type: none; border: 1em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240); font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &#39;Andale Mono&#39;, monospace; border-top-left-radius: 20px; border-top-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-left-radius: 20px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　$ mkdir _layouts</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">进入该目录，创建一个default.html文件，作为Blog的默认模板。并在该文件中填入以下内容。</p><blockquote style=\"margin: 2em; padding: 1em; list-style-type: none; border: 1em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240); font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &#39;Andale Mono&#39;, monospace; border-top-left-radius: 20px; border-top-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-left-radius: 20px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　&lt;html&gt;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　&lt;head&gt;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　　　&lt;meta http-equiv=&quot;content-type&quot; content=&quot;text/html; charset=utf-8&quot; /&gt;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　　　&lt;title&gt;{{ page.title }}&lt;/title&gt;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　&lt;/head&gt;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　&lt;body&gt;<br/><br/>　　　　{{ content }}<br/><br/>　　&lt;/body&gt;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　&lt;/html&gt;</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">Jekyll使用<a href=\"https://github.com/shopify/liquid/wiki/liquid-for-designers\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; color: rgb(17, 34, 51);\">Liquid模板语言</a>，{{ page.title }}表示文章标题，{{ content }}表示文章内容，更多模板变量请参考<a href=\"https://github.com/mojombo/jekyll/wiki/Template-Data\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; color: rgb(17, 34, 51);\">官方文档</a>。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">目录结构变成：</p><blockquote style=\"margin: 2em; padding: 1em; list-style-type: none; border: 1em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240); font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &#39;Andale Mono&#39;, monospace; border-top-left-radius: 20px; border-top-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-left-radius: 20px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　/jekyll_demo<br/>　　　　|--　_config.yml<br/>　　　　|--　_layouts<br/>　　　　|　　　|--　default.html</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 800;\">第四步，创建文章。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">回到项目根目录，创建一个_posts目录，用于存放blog文章。</p><blockquote style=\"margin: 2em; padding: 1em; list-style-type: none; border: 1em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240); font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &#39;Andale Mono&#39;, monospace; border-top-left-radius: 20px; border-top-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-left-radius: 20px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　$ mkdir _posts</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">进入该目录，创建第一篇文章。文章就是普通的文本文件，文件名假定为2012-08-25-hello-world.html。(注意，文件名必须为&quot;年-月-日-文章标题.后缀名&quot;的格式。如果网页代码采用html格式，后缀名为html；如果采用<a href=\"http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; color: rgb(17, 34, 51);\">markdown</a>格式，后缀名为md。）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">在该文件中，填入以下内容：（注意，行首不能有空格）</p><blockquote style=\"margin: 2em; padding: 1em; list-style-type: none; border: 1em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240); font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &#39;Andale Mono&#39;, monospace; border-top-left-radius: 20px; border-top-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-left-radius: 20px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　---<br/>　　layout: default<br/>　　title: 你好，世界<br/>　　---</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　&lt;h2&gt;{{ page.title }}&lt;/h2&gt;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　&lt;p&gt;我的第一篇文章&lt;/p&gt;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　&lt;p&gt;{{ page.date | date_to_string }}&lt;/p&gt;</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">每篇文章的头部，必须有一个<a href=\"https://github.com/mojombo/jekyll/wiki/YAML-Front-Matter\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; color: rgb(17, 34, 51);\">yaml文件头</a>，用来设置一些元数据。它用三根短划线&quot;---&quot;，标记开始和结束，里面每一行设置一种元数据。&quot;layout:default&quot;，表示该文章的模板使用_layouts目录下的default.html文件；&quot;title: 你好，世界&quot;，表示该文章的标题是&quot;你好，世界&quot;，如果不设置这个值，默认使用嵌入文件名的标题，即&quot;hello world&quot;。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">在yaml文件头后面，就是文章的正式内容，里面可以使用模板变量。{{ page.title }}就是文件头中设置的&quot;你好，世界&quot;，{{ page.date }}则是嵌入文件名的日期（也可以在文件头重新定义date变量），&quot;| date_to_string&quot;表示将page.date变量转化成人类可读的格式。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">目录结构变成：</p><blockquote style=\"margin: 2em; padding: 1em; list-style-type: none; border: 1em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240); font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &#39;Andale Mono&#39;, monospace; border-top-left-radius: 20px; border-top-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-left-radius: 20px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　/jekyll_demo<br/>　　　　|--　_config.yml<br/>　　　　|--　_layouts<br/>　　　　|　　　|--　default.html&nbsp;<br/>　　　　|--　_posts<br/>　　　　|　　　|--　2012-08-25-hello-world.html</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 800;\">第五步，创建首页。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">有了文章以后，还需要有一个首页。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">回到根目录，创建一个index.html文件，填入以下内容。</p><blockquote style=\"margin: 2em; padding: 1em; list-style-type: none; border: 1em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240); font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &#39;Andale Mono&#39;, monospace; border-top-left-radius: 20px; border-top-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-left-radius: 20px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　---<br/>　　layout: default<br/>　　title: 我的Blog<br/>　　---</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　&lt;h2&gt;{{ page.title }}&lt;/h2&gt;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　&lt;p&gt;最新文章&lt;/p&gt;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　&lt;ul&gt;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　　　{% for post in site.posts %}</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　　　　　&lt;li&gt;{{ post.date | date_to_string }} &lt;a href=&quot;{{ site.baseurl }}{{ post.url }}&quot;&gt;{{ post.title }}&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　　　{% endfor %}</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　&lt;/ul&gt;</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">它的Yaml文件头表示，首页使用default模板，标题为&quot;我的Blog&quot;。然后，首页使用了{% for post in site.posts %}，表示对所有帖子进行一个遍历。这里要注意的是，Liquid模板语言规定，输出内容使用两层大括号，单纯的命令使用一层大括号。至于{{site.baseurl}}就是_config.yml中设置的baseurl变量。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">目录结构变成：</p><blockquote style=\"margin: 2em; padding: 1em; list-style-type: none; border: 1em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240); font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &#39;Andale Mono&#39;, monospace; border-top-left-radius: 20px; border-top-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-left-radius: 20px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　/jekyll_demo<br/>　　　　|--　_config.yml<br/>　　　　|--　_layouts<br/>　　　　|　　　|--　default.html&nbsp;<br/>　　　　|--　_posts<br/>　　　　|　　　|--　2012-08-25-hello-world.html<br/>　　　　|--　index.html</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 800;\">第六步，发布内容。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">现在，这个简单的Blog就可以发布了。先把所有内容加入本地git库。</p><blockquote style=\"margin: 2em; padding: 1em; list-style-type: none; border: 1em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240); font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &#39;Andale Mono&#39;, monospace; border-top-left-radius: 20px; border-top-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-left-radius: 20px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　$ git add .</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　$ git commit -m &quot;first post&quot;</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">然后，前往github的网站，在网站上创建一个名为jekyll_demo的库。接着，再将本地内容推送到github上你刚创建的库。注意，下面命令中的username，要替换成你的username。</p><blockquote style=\"margin: 2em; padding: 1em; list-style-type: none; border: 1em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); background-color: rgb(245, 242, 240); font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &#39;Andale Mono&#39;, monospace; border-top-left-radius: 20px; border-top-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-left-radius: 20px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　$ git remote add origin https://github.com/<span style=\"font-weight: 800;\">username</span>/jekyll_demo.git</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">　　$ git push origin gh-pages</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">上传成功之后，等10分钟左右，访问<span style=\"font-weight: 800;\">http://username.github.com/jekyll_demo/</span>就可以看到Blog已经生成了（将username换成你的用户名）。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">首页：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\"><img src=\"http://image.beekka.com/blog/201208/bg2012082506.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0.7em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); border-top-left-radius: 0.7em; border-top-right-radius: 0.7em; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.7em; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.7em;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">文章页面：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\"><img src=\"http://image.beekka.com/blog/201208/bg2012082507.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0.7em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); border-top-left-radius: 0.7em; border-top-right-radius: 0.7em; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.7em; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.7em;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 800;\">第七步，绑定域名。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">如果你不想用<span style=\"font-weight: 800;\">http://username.github.com/jekyll_demo/</span>这个域名，可以换成自己的域名。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">具体方法是在repo的根目录下面，新建一个名为CNAME的文本文件，里面写入你要绑定的域名，比如example.com或者xxx.example.com。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">如果绑定的是顶级域名，则DNS要新建一条A记录，指向204.232.175.78。如果绑定的是二级域名，则DNS要新建一条CNAME记录，指向username.github.com（请将username换成你的用户名）。此外，别忘了将_config.yml文件中的baseurl改成根目录&quot;/&quot;。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">至此，最简单的Blog就算搭建完成了。进一步的完善，请参考Jekyll创始人的<a href=\"https://github.com/mojombo/tpw\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; color: rgb(17, 34, 51);\">示例库</a>，以及其他用Jekyll搭建的<a href=\"https://github.com/mojombo/jekyll/wiki/Sites\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; color: rgb(17, 34, 51);\">blog</a>。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; font-size: 1.6em; line-height: 28.799999237060547px;\">（完）</p><p><br/></p>', '', 'github', 0, '', 0, '0');
INSERT INTO `onethink_cms_document_article` VALUES (53, '<p><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 74, 84); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size:3px;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700;\"><a href=\"http://www.mi.com/hezi\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"relatedlink\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 102, 153); outline: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: blue;\">小米盒子</a>能用网线连接，也能用无线连接，把盒子变身WIFI热点，再也不用担心卧室信号差了！<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><p><img isfirst=\"1\" id=\"aimg_5581099\" aid=\"5581099\" src=\"http://img06.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1XnZvByDT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img06.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1XnZvByDT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" file=\"http://img06.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1XnZvByDT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"160\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" height=\"160\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; cursor: pointer;\"/></p></ignore_js_op><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/>步骤<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/>1、首先将小米盒子插好电源，连上网线，然后用HDMI线连接<a href=\"http://www.mi.com/mitv\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"relatedlink\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 102, 153); outline: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: blue;\">电视</a>。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/>2、开机后，选择主菜单&quot;应用&quot;，进入“沙发管家”软件市场。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><p><img isfirst=\"1\" id=\"aimg_5581164\" aid=\"5581164\" src=\"http://img06.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1cah_ByCT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img06.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1cah_ByCT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" file=\"http://img06.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1cah_ByCT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"580\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" height=\"327\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; cursor: pointer;\"/></p></ignore_js_op><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/>3、进入沙发管家的首页后，点击右上角的放大镜图标。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><p><img isfirst=\"1\" id=\"aimg_5581176\" aid=\"5581176\" src=\"http://img08.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T13DJvByDT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img08.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T13DJvByDT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" file=\"http://img08.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T13DJvByDT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"495\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" height=\"280\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; cursor: pointer;\"/></p></ignore_js_op><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/>4、关键几步：<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:3px;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700;\"></span></span></span></span></p><h4 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(255, 102, 102); text-align: center;\">本帖隐藏的内容</h4><p>进入搜索页面后，输入“sz”，在右侧的结果中点击“更多非TV应用”。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><p><img isfirst=\"1\" id=\"aimg_5581211\" aid=\"5581211\" src=\"http://img06.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T10TVvByYT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img06.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T10TVvByYT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" file=\"http://img06.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T10TVvByYT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"610\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" height=\"406\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; cursor: pointer;\"/></p></ignore_js_op><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/>可以找到“设置”这个软件，按步骤安装好。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><p><img isfirst=\"1\" id=\"aimg_5581276\" aid=\"5581276\" src=\"http://img08.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T111ATBCbT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img08.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T111ATBCbT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" file=\"http://img08.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T111ATBCbT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"610\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" height=\"406\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; cursor: pointer;\"/></p></ignore_js_op><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/>有了这个软件，我们就能进入Android的原始设置界面。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/>进入设置页面，选择“无线和网络”-“更多”-“便携式热点”。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><p><img isfirst=\"1\" id=\"aimg_5581367\" aid=\"5581367\" src=\"http://img07.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1ndC_ByCT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img07.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1ndC_ByCT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" file=\"http://img07.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1ndC_ByCT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"610\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" height=\"406\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; cursor: pointer;\"/></p></ignore_js_op><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/>接着开始配置WiFi热点<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><p><img isfirst=\"1\" id=\"aimg_5581395\" aid=\"5581395\" src=\"http://img06.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1lSAvByCT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img06.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1lSAvByCT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" file=\"http://img06.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1lSAvByCT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"610\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" height=\"406\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; cursor: pointer;\"/></p></ignore_js_op><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/>配置好WiFi热点的名称和密码后，点击“保存”。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><p><img isfirst=\"1\" id=\"aimg_5581427\" aid=\"5581427\" src=\"http://img08.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1NlCTB5WT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img08.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1NlCTB5WT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" file=\"http://img08.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1NlCTB5WT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"610\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" height=\"406\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; cursor: pointer;\"/></p></ignore_js_op><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/>最后记得勾选打开WiFi热点哦。<span style=\"font-family:新宋体;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:3px;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700;\"><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><p><img isfirst=\"1\" id=\"aimg_5581436\" aid=\"5581436\" src=\"http://img06.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1xYAvByCT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img06.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1xYAvByCT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" file=\"http://img06.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1xYAvByCT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"610\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" height=\"406\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; cursor: pointer;\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span></span></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:3px;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700;\"></span></span></span></span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 74, 84); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size:3px;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/>设置完成后，使用周围的移动设备（如手机和平板电脑）搜索一下，马上就看到这个新的WiFi热点了。</span></span></span></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 74, 84); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, SimHei, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 74, 84); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size:3px;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700;\"><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><p><img isfirst=\"1\" id=\"aimg_5581463\" aid=\"5581463\" src=\"http://img07.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1XgKvByCT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img07.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1XgKvByCT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" file=\"http://img07.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1XgKvByCT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"610\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" height=\"343\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; cursor: pointer;\"/></p></ignore_js_op><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/>输入密码连接成功后，就可以用手机、平板电脑尽情享受WiFi网络啦！<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/>WiFi连接速度如何？用网速测试软件测试一下，恩还不错。@JOY兔兔 @Hai_张小帅 @临阁听雨&nbsp;</span></span></span></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 74, 84); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, SimHei, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 74, 84); font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size:3px;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700;\"><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><p><img isfirst=\"1\" id=\"aimg_5581473\" aid=\"5581473\" src=\"http://img06.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1lIWTBC_T1RXrhCrK.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img06.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1lIWTBC_T1RXrhCrK.jpg\" file=\"http://img06.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1lIWTBC_T1RXrhCrK.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"610\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" height=\"343\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; cursor: pointer;\"/></p></ignore_js_op></span></span></span></span></p><p><br/></p>', '', '小米盒子', 0, '', 0, '0');
INSERT INTO `onethink_cms_document_article` VALUES (54, '<p>对于很多想要入手或刚入手<a href=\"http://www.mi.com/hezi\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"relatedlink\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 102, 153); outline: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: blue;\">小米盒子</a>的盒粉们来说，最纠结的就是不知道自己能否安装第三方应用而使盒子实现传说中的神奇功能，如果没有高手指点，往往会被某宝上那些非小米官方店家忽悠花高价去买所谓的越狱版盒子，号称可以看这看那，实际也就是给你预装了几个第三方播放器而已。然而，这些雕虫小技早已不是什么秘密，小米盒子早就给你准备好了简单方便的多种方法供你选择使用。从最早的通过‘数据线’连接电脑，到通过‘OTG’线连接U盘，再到免去任何连接的‘远程安装’一应俱全。今天我们就来普及一下目前小米盒子安装‘第一个’第三方应用的最佳方案：‘远程安装’。为什么说它是最佳？因为它只要通过盒子遥控器，在沙发上简单按几下就可以把预先下载保存在电脑里的第三方应用轻而易举地装到盒子里，不用任何连线也不需要任何通讯软件。</p><p>好了，长话短说，跟着我往下看。操作前提是在同一个wifi环境下，先打开电脑（里面已下载保存了你所需要的第三方应用，例如：沙发管家等）。</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"></ignore_js_op></p><p><img isfirst=\"1\" id=\"aimg_5550188\" aid=\"5550188\" src=\"http://img07.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1WeWTBgET1RXrhCrK.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img07.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1WeWTBgET1RXrhCrK.jpg\" file=\"http://img07.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1WeWTBgET1RXrhCrK.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"472\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" height=\"271\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; cursor: pointer;\"/></p><p></p><p><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:4px;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;word-wrap: break-word;\">小米盒子提供的远程安装实际上有两个操作方法：</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:3px;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;word-wrap: break-word;\">第一大法：电脑浏览器安装法</span></span></span></p><p>1.&nbsp; &nbsp; 在小米盒子主页上选择‘应用’栏目，进入‘应用商店’</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"></ignore_js_op></p><p><img isfirst=\"1\" id=\"aimg_5550143\" aid=\"5550143\" src=\"http://img07.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1x7CvByJT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img07.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1x7CvByJT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" file=\"http://img07.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1x7CvByJT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"610\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" height=\"343\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; cursor: pointer;\"/></p><p></p><p>2.&nbsp; &nbsp; 再进入‘应用管理’</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"></ignore_js_op></p><p><img isfirst=\"1\" id=\"aimg_5550203\" aid=\"5550203\" src=\"http://img08.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1fbWvByhT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img08.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1fbWvByhT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" file=\"http://img08.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1fbWvByhT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"610\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" height=\"343\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; cursor: pointer;\"/></p><p></p><p>3.&nbsp; &nbsp; 选择‘远程安装’</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"></ignore_js_op></p><p><img isfirst=\"1\" id=\"aimg_5550205\" aid=\"5550205\" src=\"http://img07.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T19ddvByhT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img07.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T19ddvByhT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" file=\"http://img07.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T19ddvByhT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"610\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" height=\"343\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; cursor: pointer;\"/></p><p></p><p>4.&nbsp; &nbsp; 根据提示记录大屏幕上的网址：http://........&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"></ignore_js_op></p><p><img isfirst=\"1\" id=\"aimg_5550206\" aid=\"5550206\" src=\"http://img07.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1TOLvByhT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img07.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1TOLvByhT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" file=\"http://img07.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1TOLvByhT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"610\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" height=\"343\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; cursor: pointer;\"/></p><p></p><p><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 12px;\">5.&nbsp; &nbsp; 到你的电脑上，打开浏览器，输入你刚才记录下的网址，看到什么了吗？</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"></ignore_js_op></span></span></p><p><img isfirst=\"1\" id=\"aimg_5550209\" aid=\"5550209\" src=\"http://img08.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1xtVvB4AT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img08.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1xtVvB4AT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" file=\"http://img08.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1xtVvB4AT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"610\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" height=\"343\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; cursor: pointer;\"/></p><p></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&amp;quot;;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 9pt;\">接下来点‘浏览’，找到你保存应用的文件夹，选中、打开，稍等片刻，回到小米盒子应用栏目下，你的第三方应用已经装在里面了，简单吧！</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&amp;quot;;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 9pt;\"></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size:3px;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;word-wrap: break-word;\">第二大法：与电脑‘共享’安装法</span></span></span></p><p><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><h4 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(255, 102, 102); text-align: center;\">本帖隐藏的内容</h4><p>1.&nbsp; &nbsp; 同样在小米盒子主页上选择‘应用’栏目，但这次进入的是‘高清播放器’</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"></ignore_js_op></p><p><img isfirst=\"1\" id=\"aimg_5550219\" aid=\"5550219\" src=\"http://img06.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T170LvBXxT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img06.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T170LvBXxT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" file=\"http://img06.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T170LvBXxT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"610\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" height=\"343\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; cursor: pointer;\"/></p><p></p><p>2.&nbsp; &nbsp; 找到自己的电脑（同一wifi环境下已开机的电脑很容易被小米盒子找到噢）</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"></ignore_js_op></p><p><img isfirst=\"1\" id=\"aimg_5550220\" aid=\"5550220\" src=\"http://img06.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1BAEvByJT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img06.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1BAEvByJT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" file=\"http://img06.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1BAEvByJT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"610\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" height=\"343\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; cursor: pointer;\"/></p><p></p><p><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p>3.&nbsp; &nbsp; 进入已经被‘共享’的保存有第三方应用的文件夹</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"></ignore_js_op></p><p><img isfirst=\"1\" id=\"aimg_5550221\" aid=\"5550221\" src=\"http://img07.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1fbCvByJT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img07.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1fbCvByJT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" file=\"http://img07.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1fbCvByJT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"610\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" height=\"343\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; cursor: pointer;\"/></p><p></p><p>4.&nbsp; &nbsp; 选中你要安装的app</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"></ignore_js_op></p><p><img isfirst=\"1\" id=\"aimg_5550222\" aid=\"5550222\" src=\"http://img07.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1dlLvByhT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img07.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1dlLvByhT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" file=\"http://img07.mifile.cn/v1/MI_55950AFBBEDCB/T1dlLvByhT1RXrhCrK.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"610\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" height=\"343\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; cursor: pointer;\"/></p><p></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&amp;quot;;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 9pt;\">确认安装后，回到应用栏目，OK，看到你自己装的宝贝了吧！这个方法比较第一大法是不是又省了一步到电脑上操作的步骤？挑你自己喜欢的试试啦！</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&amp;quot;;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 9pt;\">至于如何在电脑上建立‘共享’文件夹，去看看下面链接有详细步骤：</span></span></p><p><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 74, 84); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, SimHei, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&amp;quot;;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 9pt;\"><a href=\"http://bbs.xiaomi.cn/thread-9755709-1-1.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 102, 153); outline: none;\">http://bbs.xiaomi.cn/thread-9755709-1-1.html</a></span></span></p><p><br/></p>', '', '', 0, '', 0, '0');
