INSERT INTO `onethink_plugin_movie` VALUES (3364829, '太空堡垒卡拉狄加：敌人的面孔', NULL, 'http://movie.douban.com/subject/3364829/', 'null', '9.0', '', 'movie', 1398396933, 0, 0, '　　The 10 webisodes, entitled \"The Face of the Enemy,\" tell a story that takes place between seasons 4.0 and 4.5 of Battlestar and follow Lt. Gaeta when he is sent off in a Raptor with a handful of strangers and one of them mysteriously dies. The psychological human-vs.-Cylon struggle is played out in the restrictive confines of a Raptor as everyone is a suspect, and paranoia sets in among the group. *As the plot summary itself states, this summary is for BSG: The Face of the Enemy, not for BSG: The Resistance. Moving the summary to the correct title page.', 0);
