INSERT INTO `onethink_plugin_movie` VALUES (3802874, '1', NULL, 'http://movie.douban.com/subject/3802874/', 'null', '9.0', '', 'movie', 1398409233, 0, 0, '　　At twenty-five years old, the world seems pretty daunting - work, friends, love - every decision you make feels like life or death, because every decision shapes the course your life will take. At twenty-five years old, you either find the courage to pursue your dreams or make certain compromises in your career and relationships that will affect you for the next 25 years. And for six friends in Chicago, living together makes the trauma of being twenty-five years old just a little bit easier. The seven guys and girls sharing this Chicago home are caught between youth and adulthood. While some are more lost than others, each of them brings a distinct point of view about what it\'s like to try and find yourself in your twenties. Some dream about making it big, some dream about finding their soul-mate - and others are just trying to make it through the day. The one thing they all have in common is a vague notion that there\'s something more to life, but none of them are quite sure what or how to get it. Though they don\'t know it yet - this group of friends is living through the best time of their lives. From the creators of Once & Again, thirtysomething, and My So-Called Life comes a lively drama with all the promise and angst, confidence and doubt that comes with taking your first steps into adulthood', 0);
INSERT INTO `onethink_plugin_movie` VALUES (1959877, '悬崖上的金鱼姬', NULL, 'http://movie.douban.com/subject/1959877/', 'a:3:{s:5:\"small\";s:13:\"s_1959877.jpg\";s:6:\"medium\";s:13:\"m_1959877.jpg\";s:5:\"large\";s:13:\"l_1959877.jpg\";}', '9.0', '2008', 'movie', 1253376000, 0, 1, '　　金鱼姬是一条活泼好动的小鱼，一次偶然的机会，它在涨潮时被冲进了玻璃瓶中无法脱身。此时，刚好来海边度假的男孩宗介路过，帮它解困，从此人鱼相识。宗介把金鱼抱回家里喂养，一起玩耍，感情甚笃。由于海员父亲终日出航，宗介只得跟母亲相依为命，这让他的性格孤僻自闭，甚至对长辈也不理不睬。但是，遇到金鱼姬后，宗介逐渐改变了对生活的冷漠态度，这也让他慢慢修复了性格中的缺陷。一次意外的海啸中，宗介撞伤了身体，金鱼姬沾染到了人类的血，飘回了大海之中。原来海洋中还有另外一个世界，那里有个操控水文环境的古怪男子藤本，因为发现了人类污染环境的丑陋，所以自造了另一个水中世界。他发现金鱼姬沾染了人气，正准备用魔法将它打回原形，却事与愿违……', 0);
